## 🛠 Routine for the next BEARWATCH session

1. Read this STATUS.md first to know what's running and what's pending
2. Do the requested work
3. **Before declaring done:** update this file's "Live right now", "Recently completed", and "Open questions" sections
4. Commit STATUS.md change as part of the session's commits
